'''Perigen''' was a non-narcotic [[Painkiller/Legends|painkiller]] that could be applied in patch form<ref name="CotJ">[[Children of the Jedi (novel)|''Children of the Jedi'']]</ref> and via an epidural. Members of the [[Pui-ui]] [[Species/Legends|species]] had a fatal allergy to perigen.<ref name="EGTD">''[[The Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref> [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] used a perigen patch aboard the ''[[Eye of Palpatine]]'' to lessen the pain of his injured [[Limb/Legends|leg]].<ref name="CotJ" />

